descript.abstract: This file was created in 2006 by combining New York, New Jersey, and Connecticut shapefiles. The original file suffered from overlapping and misalighed polygons. Therefore, the file was modified in 2008 using ArcMap Editor to merge the polygons for a more unified shapefile.
descript.purpose: The data was created as a regional water shapefile for New York, New Jesery, and Connecticut.
